content: Email button doesn't work and personal photo gallery needs work. Most recent photos are last making it difficult to find photos. Also the folders don't seem to have any particular order. How about most recent to least for folders AND photos? Please fix. Also, would like the ability to save pics in PNG transparent background so that I can edit my own individual characters.
replyContent: I'll check the email button. Also do you think the default system photo gallery will do the job? If yes I'll replace it. About saving with transparent background, you can change the opacity of the background color to transparent using the background color option (at the right of the lock button). Thanks for the suggestions!
